headline: AOS Q4 Deep Dive: Margin Expansion Amid Flat Sales and Strategic Portfolio Moves
summary: Water heating and treatment solutions company A.O. Smith (NYSE:AOS) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales flat year on year at $912.5 million. The company’s full-year revenue guidance of $3.96 billion at the midpoint came in 1.3% below analysts’ estimates. Its GAAP profit of $0.90 per share was 5.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
